VNC Server Configuration
========================

Port: {{ vnc_port }}
Display: :{{ vnc_display }}
Resolution: {{ vnc_geometry }}
Desktop: XFCE4

Password: {{ vnc_password }}

Management Commands:
  Start VNC:  start-vnc
  Stop VNC:   stop-vnc
  Status:     sudo systemctl status vncserver@{{ vnc_display }}.service
  Restart:    sudo systemctl restart vncserver@{{ vnc_display }}.service

Manual Commands:
  Start:  vncserver :{{ vnc_display }} -geometry {{ vnc_geometry }} -depth {{ vnc_depth }}
  Stop:   vncserver -kill :{{ vnc_display }}
  List:   vncserver -list

Connecting:
  VNC Viewer: <instance-ip>:{{ vnc_port }}
  Password: (see above)

Troubleshooting:
  View logs: journalctl -u vncserver@{{ vnc_display }}.service -f
  Kill all:  vncserver -kill :*
  Reset:     rm -rf ~/.vnc/*.pid ~/.vnc/*.log
